Directed by Santiago Korovsky. Diego Nuñez Irigoyen.

Written by Ignacio Gaggero. Martín Garabal. Santiago Korovsky. Martina López Robol. Florencia Percia. Ignacio Sánchez Mestre. Mariana Wainstein.

Cast Pilar Gamboa. Daniel Hendler. Martín Garabal. Marcelo Subiotto. Carlos Belloso. Charo López. Sergio Prina. Agustín Rittano. Valeria Lois. Alan Sabbagh. Rafael Spregelburd. Valeria Licciardi. Iair Said. Nilda Sindaco. Camila Peralta. Jonathan Jairo Nugnes. Gabriela Izcovich. Fabián Arenillas. Daniela Korovsky. Julio Marticorena. Hernán Cuevas. Facundo Bogarin. Alicia Labraga.

Language Spanish.

Production K&S Films.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 8

Status On Going (2023–)
